{"type":"assistant.message","data":{"messageId":"97087ce1-9cf6-42e4-b154-3918c0cd0c4e","content":"There's no relevant documentation in the current workspace, but here's the general approach for macOS:\n\n### Recovering a crash dump on macOS without `createdump`\n\n1. **Check for macOS system crash reports** — when a process crashes, macOS writes reports to:\n   ```\n   ~/Library/Logs/DiagnosticReports/\n   /Library/Logs/DiagnosticReports/\n   ```\n   Look for files named `<YourApp>_<date>_<host>.ips` or `.crash`.\n\n2. **Enable core dumps** before reproducing:\n   ```bash\n   ulimit -c unlimited\n   sudo sysctl kern.corefile=/tmp/core.%P\n   ```\n   Then re-run your app. The core file will be written to `/tmp/core.<pid>`.\n\n3. **Check if SIP blocks core dumps** — on modern macOS, System Integrity Protection can prevent core dump generation. You may need to disable it for debugging (via Recovery Mode → `csrutil disable`), or sign your binary with the `com.apple.security.get-task-allow` entitlement:\n   ```bash\n   codesign -s - --entitlements entitlements.plist ./YourApp\n   ```\n   where `entitlements.plist` includes `com.apple.security.get-task-allow = true`.\n\n4. **Analyze the dump** with `lldb`:\n   ```bash\n   lldb --core /tmp/core.<pid> ./YourApp\n   ```\n\n5. **Alternative — use `lldb` directly** to catch the crash live:\n   ```bash\n   lldb ./YourApp\n   (lldb) run\n   # after crash:\n   (lldb) bt        # backtrace\n   (lldb) process save-core /tmp/myapp.core\n   ```\n\nThe key macOS-specific gotcha is that **SIP and code-signing entitlements** often silently prevent core dump creation, so step 3 is usually the missing piece.","toolRequests":[],"interactionId":"d6d20bec-94fb-41f2-bb53-8eae50d65765","reasoningOpaque":"","reasoningText":"The working directory appears to be empty or has no visible files. This question isn't about the repository — it's a general knowledge question about macOS crash dumps for NativeAOT apps. Let me answer from my knowledge.","outputTokens":534,"requestId":"5024:5409:26DECF:30B2F1:69F554DE"},"id":"1ae3ea41-2e9f-4f17-a8e4-ba61e97b369a","timestamp":"2026-05-02T01:35:38.902Z","parentId":"3f02ffd2-8aff-470e-8e7a-cdea3ec46cfb"}
